Download Java using below command
<p><b>wget --no-cookies --no-check-certificate --header "Cookie: gpw_e24=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oracle.com%2F; oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie" "http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/8u131-b11/d54c1d3a095b4ff2b6607d096fa80163/jdk-8u131-linux-x64.rpm"</b></p>
After the download is complete locate the rpm file and then install it using <p>rpm -Uvh jdk-8u131-linux-x64.rpm</p>
Set the environmental varibles
Edit .bash_profile and paste the below commands
export JAVA_HOME=java install location
export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH
source .bash_profile


